            <div class="w-full">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">낙찰하한율 <span class="text-xs font-normal bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">2025.7.1 예규 개정</span></h4>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">
                <div class="p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-100">
